Energy Hunter Resources Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















energy hunter resources inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Energy
Industry: Oil, Gas & Coal
Sub-Industry: Exploration & Production
Energy Hunter Resources, Inc. focuses on oil exploration and production. The Company owns and operates oil properties, as well as offers horizontal drilling and fracture stimulation technology. Energy Hunter Resources serves customers in the United States.




