Industry News


                Energy            


New Dallas-based energy co. led by former Magnum Hunter CEO opens Houston office




Sep 19, 2016, 12:55pm CDT



Updated Sep 21, 2016, 4:26pm CDT






Industries & Tags


                    Energy,                 


            Oil & gas             














Olivia Pulsinelli


Senior web editor
Houston Business Journal













