Energy Hunter Resources, Inc. |   About






































































































































About
 Home / About









Our MissionEnergy Hunter Resources, Inc. is an independent, oil-focused exploration and production company headquartered in Dallas, Texas with a mission to own and operate properties within some of the most prolific resource plays in the United States. Initially focusing on the Eagle Ford Shale and Permian Basin, our aim is to create substantial shareholder value through a balanced program of acquisitions and low-risk development and exploitation opportunities utilizing horizontal drilling and fracture stimulation technology.



























Energy Hunter Resources, Inc. | 





































































































































